<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000" ALINK="#FF00FF">
<CENTER><B><U>Table of Authorities</U></B></CENTER>
<P><B><U>Cases</U></B>
<P><I>Employment Division, Department of Human Resources of Oregon v.
Smith</I>
<BR>1990) 494 U.S. 872
<BR>108 L.Ed.2d 876
<BR>110 S.Ct. 1595

